compulsions and emotional storms they can't understand the unconscious doesn't simply disappear when ignored it breaks through in destructive ways consider the phenomenon of what young called the shadow all the parts of yourself you've repressed or denied your anger your shame your forbidden desires

34
00:05:39,286 --> 00:05:50,000
your unacknowledged capacities. In traditional cultures, there were rituals specifically designed to acknowledge and integrate these shadow aspects.

35
00:05:50,922 --> 00:06:06,423
Carnival, for instance, was a sanctioned time when social rules could be inverted, when people could temporarily embrace their shadow sides in a contained symbolic way before returning to normal life.

36
00:06:06,944 --> 00:06:18,471
