00:06:19,435 --> 00:06:22,422
Millions of civilized Europeans.

38
00:06:22,755 --> 00:06:40,173
having repressed their primal instincts and darker impulses in the name of rationality and progress, suddenly became possessed by these forces on a massive scale, the unconscious, denied proper ritual expression,

