68
00:11:23,203 --> 00:11:32,047
The eternal flame of spirit, none of which we think consciously. but all of which our unconscious recognizes.

69
00:11:33,008 --> 00:11:41,817
Jung emphasized that symbols can't be created intellectually. They must emerge from the unconscious and carry emotional resonance.

70
00:11:42,719 --> 00:11:52,870
Third, repetition with presence. Rituals gain power through repetition, but this isn't mechanical repetition.

71
00:11:53,611 --> 00:12:04,652
